Use Case
	AsteroidSplit
Actors
	Asteroid,system
Description
	the system asks the asteroid to split.
Main Course of Events
Actor	System
		1.The system has determined that the asteroid shall split
 		2.The system Asks for the asteroids heading,size and speed.
3.Provides
		4.The system checks if the size is the not smallest one
		5.The system creates 2 new smaller asteroids with half of the speed of the original
			and heading mirrored an angle along the old asteroids heading 

Alternative Flow of Events
4.1 the asteroid is of the smallest type. The asteroid dies.